---
title: Spiced Chicken & Tahini Crushed Potatoes with Slaw & Spring Onion
description: A potato crush is a party you don’t want to miss, with a special guest appearance from a tasty tahini sauce it’s going
to be a blast! The party doesn’t start though until the herby garlic chicken enters the room. Now get those forks grooving
and dig in.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
